[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Initial longitudinal-store assembly]                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions across providers                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reconciled medication list                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Allergies                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care plan elements                                   │
