[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open referrals                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open authorizations                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled appointments                               │
