[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team across organizations                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Plan benefits and coverage                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinants context                          │
