[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Authoritative-source-of-truth reconciliation]          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Apply institutional precedence rules per data class  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Flag discrepancies for human resolution              │
